    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and budget-friendly daily driver? This vehicle is ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid performer that's been well-maintained to keep you moving. It's the perfect choice for someone who values dependability and great value over a showroom finish!",
