    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is. It requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be reliable. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust on the rocker panels, several deep scratches, and a large dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the electronics are inconsistent. This would be a suitable project for someone with the skills to perform extensive repairs.",
